  <bioghist id="aspace_12ccaedf9d1bc47235508019e5831617">
    <head>BIOGRAPHICAL NOTE</head>
<p>Emil A. Kohm was born in Germany and worked as a tailor in Ithaca, New York.</p>  </bioghist>
  <scopecontent id="aspace_73cbcb2949af805c3dc70355350b2ba9">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Customers' accounts, cashbooks, and wage records (6 vols.); also, letters and accounts concerning the tailoring business, the settlement of the Kohm estate, and other matters.</p>  </scopecontent>
